:宋体; font-size:12pt">拥有一支专业的、经验丰富的区块链技术及运营团队，致力于为全球</span><span style="color:#2f2f2f; font-family:宋体; font-size:12pt">加密货币</span><span style="color:#2f2f2f; font-family:宋体; font-size:12pt">合约交易用户提供一个安全、便捷、稳定、低交易成本的平台。</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:15.75pt; widows:0"><span style="color:#2f2f2f; font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="color:#2f2f2f; font-family:宋体; font-size:12pt"> 所有交易合约标的均以</span><span style="color:#2f2f2f; font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">USDT </span><span style="color:#2f2f2f; font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="color:#2f2f2f; font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">(</span><span style="color:#2f2f2f; font-family:宋体; font-size:12pt">简称</span><span style="color:#2f2f2f; font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">:</span><span style="color:#2f2f2f; font-family:宋体; font-size:12pt">泰达币</span><span style="color:#2f2f2f; font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">)</span><span style="color:#2f2f2f; font-family:宋体; font-size:12pt">进行报价及结算，所有账户的保证金及结算均不支持任何法币</span><span style="color:#2f2f2f; font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">(</span><span style="color:#2f2f2f; font-family:宋体; font-size:12pt">例如人 民币或美元</span><span style="color:#2f2f2f; font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">)</span><span style="color:#2f2f2f; font-family:宋体; font-size:12pt">，平台提供区块</span><span style="color:#2f2f2f; font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">OMNI</span><span style="color:#2f2f2f; font-family:宋体; font-size:12pt">数字钱包服务，每个用户独立生成</span><span style="color:#2f2f2f; font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">OMNI</span><span style="color:#2f2f2f; font-family:宋体; font-size:12pt">数字钱包与账户绑定，对接全球区块网络，全球所有区块平台无缝对接，支持和所有平台间的</span><span style="color:#2f2f2f; font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">USDT</span><span style="color:#2f2f2f; font-family:宋体; font-size:12pt">划转，为所有交易用户提供便捷、安全、有效的账户划转、结算。</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; orphans:0; text-align:jus