nt-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10.5pt">USDT</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">，</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10.5pt">B </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">用户个人需要 </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10.5pt">USDT</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">，那么 </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10.5pt">A </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">用户通过平台进行发布出售 </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10.5pt">USDT </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">信息，</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10.5pt">B </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">用户在平台提交购买 </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10.5pt">USDT </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">的需求，系统将 </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10.5pt">A </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">用户与 </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10.5pt">B </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">用户进行匹配，此时 </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10.5pt">B </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">用户把人民币转给 </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10.5pt">A </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">用 户，</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10.5pt">A </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">用户把 </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10.5pt">USDT </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">币转给 </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10.5pt">B </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">用户，此笔交易完成，平台方在此承担着监督与担 保的作用，以防其中一方违约等事项，但平台方不参与任何一方人民币的经手操 作，完全由 </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10.5pt">AB </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-